    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A soft, friable, earthy stone of light gray to olive color, used as an abrasive for metal and wood finishing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
